Tue Jun 16 13:22:54 UTC 2026 - Richard Rahl <rrahl0@opensuse.org>

- Update to version 1.1.15:
  + Fix: 127.0.0.1 is not loopback
  + Higher default bandwidth
  + Define the HOME env to allow running rootless
  + Connection log query
  + Add option to log (failed) authentication attempts to enable the usage of
    tools like fail2ban and crowdsec
- remove %cargo_install macro, so we don't build the software twice

